09:53.676 --> 09:55.468
GET 'EM!

09:56.220 --> 09:58.305
GET 'EM!

09:58.723 --> 10:01.224
GEORGE!

10:01.392 --> 10:03.518
GET 'EM!

10:03.686 --> 10:05.061
[INDISTINCT SHOUTING]

10:05.229 --> 10:06.980
YOU'LL PAY FOR THIS,
YOU FREAKS!

10:07.148 --> 10:10.817
