11:59.635 --> 12:01.720
[TIRES SCREECH]

12:01.887 --> 12:03.388
VIRGINIA!

12:03.556 --> 12:05.432
COME BACK!

12:06.142 --> 12:07.517
GINNIE, COME BACK!

12:07.685 --> 12:08.768
VIRGINIA!

12:08.936 --> 12:10.186
