THE RIGHT TO GO VISIT

16:17.935 --> 16:19.018
MY OWN MOTHER'S GRAVE!

16:19.186 --> 16:22.563
GINNIE, GINNIE,
GINNIE, PLEASE.

16:34.994 --> 16:37.453
I'M SO SORRY.

16:37.621 --> 16:40.164
DADDY, PLEASE
DON'T BE ANGRY WITH ME.

16:45.504 --> 16:48.506
YOU CAN'T LIVE
IN THE PAST, HONEY.

16:49.341 --> 16:52.427
DADDY, I HAVE TO REMEMBER.

16:52.594 --> 16:55.179
