REPRESSING WHAT HAPPENED,

16:55.347 --> 16:59.392
I-I WON'T BE COMPLETELY CURED.

16:59.560 --> 17:02.395
HE SAYS I'M PROGRESSING
VERY QUICKLY.

17:02.563 --> 17:05.815
GINNIE, WE'VE
BEEN HAPPY TOGETHER.

17:05.983 --> 17:09.609
I DON'T WANT ANY OF
THOSE MEMORIES TO CHANGE THAT.

17:10.319 --> 17:12.363
OH, GOD.

17:12.531 --> 17:15.867
SOMETIMES I WISH WE'D
NEVER MOVED BACK HERE.

17:16.242 --> 17:19.412
I LOVE THIS HOUSE.

17:19.579 --> 17:25.209
I LIKE LIVING HERE.

17:25.377 --> 17:27.920
I LIKE MY SCHOOL.

17:28.088 --> 17:31.257
I LIKE MY FRIENDS.

17:31.425 --> 17:34.135
PLEASE DON'T TAKE
THAT AWAY FROM ME.

17:35.262 --> 17:39.849
