24:43.023 --> 24:45.900
BY APPLYING THE ELECTRICAL
CHARGE OF THE GALVANIC PROBE,

24:46.067 --> 24:49.403
TO THE NERVE IN THE FROG'S
LEG... GALVANI INDUCED MUSCLE

24:49.571 --> 24:52.907
CONTRACTION, AS THOUGH
THE LEG WERE ALIVE.

24:54.117 --> 24:55.493
[LAUGHTER]

24:55.660 --> 24:58.329
WHAT'S SO FUNNY?

25:00.373 --> 25:02.958
YES, MR. VAN DER PALL,
QUITE THE COMEDIAN.

25:03.126 --> 25:05.336
BUT THE REALLY FUNNY THING
ABOUT STATIC ELECTRICITY

25:05.504 --> 25:07.630
IS THAT IT CAN BE DISCHARGED.

25:07.797 --> 25:10.049
AAAH!

25:10.550 --> 25:13.511
[LAUGHTER]

25:14.554 --> 25:16.555
NOW, LET'S GET SERIOUS.

25:16.723 --> 25:18.807
POWER, PLEASE.

25:18.975 --> 25:21.769
I APPLY THE PROBE TO
THE NERVE OF THE FROG'S LEG.

25:21.937 --> 25:24.980
[BUZZING]

25:45.335 --> 25:48.546
[MONITOR BEEPING]

25:48.713 --> 25:52.841
[HEARTBEATS]

26:08.108 --> 26:09.567
DOCTOR?

26:09.734 --> 26:11.652
DOCTOR, WHY IS
SHE DOING THAT?

26:11.820 --> 26:13.654
A RANDOM DISCHARGE,
MR. WAINWRIGHT.

26:13.822 --> 26:16.949
THE BRAIN TISSUE
IS REBUILDING ITSELF.

26:17.117 --> 26:18.617
THERE'S NO WAY OF
KNOWING WHETHER NEW TISSUE

26:18.785 --> 26:20.578
WILL FUNCTION NORMALLY OR NOT.

26:20.745 --> 26:22.580
WITHIN THE PAST YEAR, WE'VE
HAD SOME MARVELOUS RESULTS

26:22.747 --> 26:24.206
WITH A NEW TECHNIQUE.

26:24.374 --> 26:26.041
THE PRINCIPLE IS SOUND,
AND I THINK WE'LL SUCCEED

26:26.209 --> 26:27.876
WITH VIRGINIA.

26:28.044 --> 26:29.712
IN FACT, WE ARE SUCCEEDING.

26:29.879 --> 26:31.439
THEN WHEY THE HELL
ISN'T SHE CONSCIOUS?!

26:31.506 --> 26:32.746
SHE'S BEEN LIKE
THIS FOR MONTHS.

26:32.882 --> 26:34.425
SHE ONLY MOVES WHEN
YOU TURN ON THAT MACHINE!

26:34.593 --> 26:35.843
[ALARM BEEPING]

26:36.011 --> 26:37.094
DR. FEINBLUM, HER
ALPHAS ARE UP AGAIN.

26:37.262 --> 26:39.054
I'LL SWITCH OFF.

26:39.222 --> 26:42.057
WHAT'S HAPPENING?

26:42.767 --> 26:45.769
VIRGINIA, CAN YOU HEAR ME?

26:52.152 --> 26:54.987
M... M-M... M-M-MY...

26:55.155 --> 26:58.198
B-B-BIR... BIRTHDAY.

26:58.700 --> 27:04.121
I WAS AN EXPERIMENT, DAVID,
JUST LIKE THAT FROG IN THE LAB.

27:07.042 --> 27:09.335
THE PRINCIPLE
IS VERY SIMPLE.

27:09.502 --> 27:14.131
WHEN A, UH, SALAMANDER LOSES
ITS TAIL, IT GROWS A NEW ONE.

27:14.299 --> 27:20.137
AND, UH, DR. FEINBLUM FOUND
THAT WHEN THIS HAPPENS, THE

27:20.305 --> 27:24.308
SALAMANDER'S NERVOUS SYSTEM
CREATES A KIND OF ELECTRIC

27:24.476 --> 27:27.227
FIELD AROUND THE
SITE OF THE WOUND.

27:27.395 --> 27:31.649
SO WHAT HE DID WAS HE
DEVELOPED THIS APPARATUS WHICH

27:31.816 --> 27:35.653
REPRODUCED THIS
FIELD IN HUMAN BEINGS.

27:35.820 --> 27:39.114
AND THIS FIELD BROUGHT ABOUT
A REGENERATION AND A HEALING

27:39.282 --> 27:46.163
OF, UH, BROKEN BONES, DAMAGED
TISSUE, INTERNAL ORGANS.

27:46.331 --> 27:50.167
AND BRAIN CELLS.

27:50.960 --> 27:54.088
YOU WERE THE FIRST.

27:54.714 --> 27:56.298
A GUINEA PIG.

27:56.466 --> 28:01.679
YES, BUT A VERY
SUCCESSFUL GUINEA PIG.

28:01.846 --> 28:05.516
WHAT YOU REMEMBERED
TODAY PROVES IT.

28:05.975 --> 28:08.811
YOU SEE, VIRGINIA, DR. FEINBLUM
WAS CONVINCED

28:08.978 --> 28:12.898
THAT YOU... YOUR BRAIN
TISSUE HAD BEEN RESTORED

28:13.066 --> 28:15.109
BY HIS TREATMENT.

28:15.276 --> 28:16.860
AND TODAY I REMEMBERED.

28:17.028 --> 28:18.320
YES.

28:18.488 --> 28:21.657
AND TOMORROW YOU
WILL REMEMBER MORE.

28:21.825 --> 28:23.867
- EVEN THE...
- EVEN THE ACCIDENT.

28:24.035 --> 28:26.203
I-I'M NOT SAYING
IT'S GONNA BE EASY.

28:26.371 --> 28:27.871
[SIGHS]

28:28.039 --> 28:31.125
SOME OF THE MEMORIES
MAY BE VERY PAINFUL.

28:31.292 --> 28:33.502
THAT'S WHY YOU'VE
REPRESSED THEM.

28:33.670 --> 28:38.090
BUT YOU WILL REMEMBER,
VIRGINIA, AND YOU

28:38.258 --> 28:40.259
WILL BE COMPLETE.

28:40.427 --> 28:42.428
[SIGHS]

28:42.595 --> 28:45.055
SCARY.

28:45.223 --> 28:47.474
YEAH.

28:48.643 --> 28:52.646
I WON'T LET ANYTHING
OR ANYBODY HURT YOU.

29:00.113 --> 29:02.781
NO, I WON'T.

29:05.118 --> 29:08.120
SEE YA.

29:10.623 --> 29:12.833
GOODNIGHT, GINNIE.

29:17.338 --> 29:20.841
[CHEERS AND APPLAUSE]

29:23.386 --> 29:25.971
COME ON, ETIENNE!

29:27.682 --> 29:30.309
COME ON, ETIENNE!

29:34.731 --> 29:36.064
YEAH!
COME ON, BABY!

29:36.232 --> 29:38.108
THIS IS YOUR MATCH!
DO IT, BABY!

29:38.276 --> 29:41.069
YOU CAN DO IT!

29:45.992 --> 29:47.409
TAKE IT HOME!
TAKE IT HOME!

29:47.577 --> 29:48.994
TAKE IT HOME!

29:49.162 --> 29:50.329
COME ON, YOU BASTARD!

29:50.497 --> 29:52.748
WE'VE GOT 50 BUCKS ON YOU!

30:04.844 --> 30:06.220
COME ON!

30:06.387 --> 30:08.680
GO!

30:31.704 --> 30:33.080
BOOGIE DOWN, BABY!

30:33.248 --> 30:36.583
BOOGIE DOWN!

30:38.044 --> 30:41.839
[CHEERS AND APPLAUSE]

30:44.175 --> 30:45.467
YOU DID IT!

30:45.635 --> 30:46.885
YAY!

30:47.053 --> 30:48.262
FANTASTIC!

30:48.429 --> 30:49.721
DID YOU WIPE
THAT MOTHER OUT?!

30:49.889 --> 30:51.473
WHOO!

30:51.641 --> 30:53.058
HOT DAMN!

30:53.226 --> 30:54.393
4 TO 1... WE MADE 200 BUCKS!

30:54.561 --> 30:55.602
200 BUCKS?!

30:55.770 --> 30:57.354
WE ARE RICH!

30:57.522 --> 30:58.897
THIS CALLS
FOR A CELEBRATION!

30:59.065 --> 31:00.691
THE SILENT WOMAN!

31:00.859 --> 31:02.609
YOU GOT IT!

31:02.777 --> 31:04.945
BUT FIRST I HAVE
TO CLEAN UP MY BIKE.

31:05.113 --> 31:06.446
WE'LL ALL JUST
MEET THERE TONIGHT.

31:06.614 --> 31:07.698
WHAT TIME?

31:07.866 --> 31:08.949
SEVEN O'CLOCK.

31:09.117 --> 31:10.284
OKAY, SEE YOU THEN.

31:10.451 --> 31:11.994
BYE.

31:12.161 --> 31:13.961
TOO BAD BERNADETTE
WASN'T HERE TO SEE YOU WIN.

31:14.038 --> 31:15.581
I HAD TO WIN.

31:15.748 --> 31:20.669
I WAS CARRYING THIS
NEXT TO MY HEART.

31:24.257 --> 31:26.466
GOD, YOU'VE GOT
A LOT OF NERVE.

31:26.634 --> 31:28.135
THAT'S NOT ALL I'VE GOT.

31:28.303 --> 31:30.512
WANT TO SEE?

31:36.561 --> 31:39.354
WHAT THE HELL
ARE YOU LOOKING AT?

31:41.691 --> 31:43.275
GOD, THAT ETIENNE.

31:43.443 --> 31:44.735
WHAT A MOVER.

31:44.903 --> 31:46.695
NO WONDER
BERNADETTE TOOK OFF.

31:46.863 --> 31:48.155
ARE YOU KIDDING?

31:48.323 --> 31:49.615
SHE LOVES IT.

31:49.782 --> 31:51.742
DON'T YOU KNOW THAT THEY'VE
TAKEN A ROOM IN SOME

31:51.910 --> 31:53.327
SEEDY MOTEL AND ARE
DOIN' IT EVERY NIGHT?

31:53.494 --> 31:55.996
OH, COME ON, THEY ARE NOT.

31:56.164 --> 31:57.998
HOW DO YOU KNOW?

31:58.166 --> 32:00.542
AH, MY SWEET,
INNOCENT VIRGINIA.

32:00.710 --> 32:03.420
I'VE GOT A LOT TO TEACH YOU.

32:03.588 --> 32:05.964
HA.

32:17.936 --> 32:25.936
♪♪♪

32:48.383 --> 32:54.054
[MOTORCYCLE ENGINE
RUNNING]

32:57.308 --> 33:05.308
♪♪♪

33:49.402 --> 33:51.361
AAAH!

33:58.745 --> 34:00.704
[ENGINE STOPS]

34:02.957 --> 34:04.708
YOUNG WOMAN: HEY, YOU
GUYS, NO ANSWER AT ETIENNE'S.

34:04.876 --> 34:06.796
YOU THINK HE'D COME TO
HIS OWN CELEBRATION PARTY.

34:06.919 --> 34:08.837
AND WHERE THE
HELL IS ALFRED ANYWAYS?

34:09.005 --> 34:11.297
HE'S ON A NEW BIOLOGY
PROJECT... STUFFED STUDENTS.

34:11.466 --> 34:12.799
OH, COME ON, YOU GUYS.

34:12.967 --> 34:14.384
HE'S YOUR REGULAR,
ALL-AMERICAN BOY.

34:14.552 --> 34:16.887
GHOUL... ALL-AMERICAN GHOUL.

34:17.054 --> 34:18.804
COME ON, STEVE,
HE'S NOT THAT BAD.

34:18.973 --> 34:20.766
I THINK THESE
GIRLS LIKE ALFRED.

34:20.933 --> 34:23.560
I THINK THEY WOULD LIKE
TO BE STUFFED BY ALFRED.

34:23.728 --> 34:25.187
WHY DON'T YOU
GET STUFFED, RUDI?

34:25.353 --> 34:26.688
GOD, YOU'RE GROSS.

34:26.856 --> 34:28.940
JUST PISS RIGHT
OFF, MAGGIE, OKAY?

34:29.108 --> 34:31.109
RUDI, MAGGIE, LOOK...

34:31.277 --> 34:32.777
YOU GOT TO QUIT THIS
BICKERING BACK AND FORTH,

34:32.945 --> 34:34.154
ALL RIGHT?

34:34.322 --> 34:36.739
NOW, COME ON,
KISS AND MAKE UP.

34:40.286 --> 34:41.786
WELL, THERE'S
NO PROBLEM THERE.

34:41.954 --> 34:43.163
OKAY, COME ON, LET'S PARTY.

34:43.331 --> 34:44.831
THE NIGHT'S YOUNG.

34:44.998 --> 34:46.500
VIRGINIA: FOR GOD'S SAKE,
WHAT'S THIS ALL ABOUT, ANN?

34:46.667 --> 34:48.001
I DON'T WANT TO SEE ALFRED.

34:48.168 --> 34:50.449
ANYWAY, HE'S PROBABLY STILL
IN THE LAB STUFFING SOMETHING.

34:50.463 --> 34:51.838
STUFFING WHAT, I WONDER.

34:52.005 --> 34:53.632
HE HAS BEEN ACTING
VERY ODD LATELY.

34:53.800 --> 34:55.300
JUST GO AROUND THE
BACK AND KEEP WATCH, OKAY?

34:55.467 --> 34:57.761
OKAY.

34:57.929 --> 35:05.929
♪♪♪

35:14.278 --> 35:16.196
AAAH!

35:16.364 --> 35:17.989
FOOLED YA.

35:18.157 --> 35:20.951
JESUS CHRIST, YOU JUST
SCARED THE SHIT OUT OF ME.

35:21.119 --> 35:22.702
[SIGHS]

35:22.870 --> 35:24.079
IS HE IN?

35:24.247 --> 35:25.622
NO, AND THE DOOR'S LOCKED.

35:25.790 --> 35:28.291
BUT THERE IS A
WINDOW THAT'S OPEN.

35:28.459 --> 35:29.584
SO?

35:29.752 --> 35:31.503
SO WHY DON'T WE GO IN THERE
AND SEE WHAT EVIL DEEDS

35:31.671 --> 35:34.464
LITTLE ALFRED'S BEEN UP TO?

35:36.175 --> 35:44.175
♪♪♪

35:51.023 --> 35:52.190
SHH!

35:52.358 --> 35:53.358
DO YOU NEED A HAND?

35:53.484 --> 35:54.484
YES!

35:54.652 --> 35:55.443
OH.

35:55.611 --> 35:56.611
[LAUGHS]

35:56.737 --> 35:57.737
[GROANS]

35:57.738 --> 36:01.074
[MUFFLED LAUGHTER]

36:02.493 --> 36:04.744
SHH!

36:05.454 --> 36:06.663
SHH!

36:06.831 --> 36:09.791
QUIET.

36:16.841 --> 36:19.926
GOD, THIS PLACE IS
ALMOST AS WEIRD AS HE IS.

36:20.386 --> 36:22.929
THINK HE REALLY
STUFFS ALL THESE THINGS?

36:23.097 --> 36:25.682
WHO KNOWS?

36:26.309 --> 36:27.726
ANN, LET'S JUST GET
THE HELL OUT OF HERE.

36:27.894 --> 36:29.561
AH, COURAGE, MY DEAR.

36:29.729 --> 36:32.022
[SIGHS]

36:34.025 --> 36:42.025
♪♪♪

36:47.538 --> 36:50.248
HMM.

37:08.017 --> 37:10.810
WHAT IS IT?

37:10.978 --> 37:13.605
I DON'T KNOW.

37:13.773 --> 37:16.900
THERE'S ONLY
ONE WAY TO FIND OUT.

37:17.068 --> 37:18.985
NO!

37:19.695 --> 37:22.280
AAAH!

37:22.448 --> 37:24.783
OH, GOD.

37:26.327 --> 37:29.746
OH, JESUS!

37:36.212 --> 37:38.088
WINDOW!

37:38.256 --> 37:39.923
[GASPS]

37:40.091 --> 37:42.467
WHAT ARE YOU DOING HERE?

37:42.635 --> 37:46.304
WE WERE WORRIED BECAUSE
YOU DIDN'T SHOW UP AT THE INN.

37:46.472 --> 37:49.099
YOU WERE WORRIED ABOUT ME?

37:52.186 --> 37:54.896
WORRIED...

37:55.064 --> 37:57.190
ABOUT ME?

37:57.358 --> 38:01.403
MAYBE YOU WERE WORRIED
ABOUT BERNADETTE.

38:03.155 --> 38:07.659
WHAT ABOUT POOR,
LITTLE BERNADETTE?

38:07.827 --> 38:10.620
HOW DO YOU LIKE HER?

38:10.788 --> 38:13.707
MY LATEST MASTERPIECE.

38:13.874 --> 38:16.751
SHE IS A MASTERPIECE,
ISN'T SHE?

38:16.919 --> 38:21.840
I'M... I'M VERY PROUD OF HER.

38:22.008 --> 38:26.052
AND I'LL TELL YOU SOMETHING.

38:26.220 --> 38:31.599
IF YOU'RE BOTH VERY GOOD,
YOU CAN BE MY NEXT MODELS.

38:31.767 --> 38:35.228
I THINK YOU'D
BE GOOD MODELS.

38:56.334 --> 38:58.376
ANN: OH, JESUS, ALFRED.

38:58.544 --> 39:03.048
YOU MIGHT THINK THIS IS
A JOKE, BUT I THINK IT'S SICK.

39:03.215 --> 39:05.675
[VOICE ECHOING]
SICK, SICK, SICK.

39:06.469 --> 39:10.180
[BELL TOLLS]

39:19.065 --> 39:20.398
WATCH IT.

39:20.566 --> 39:21.858
SHE'S ON THE WARPATH.

39:22.026 --> 39:24.861
VIRGINIA, YOU'RE NEXT.

39:26.113 --> 39:28.823
HEY, WAIT FOR ME.

39:29.408 --> 39:30.825
[KNOCK ON DOOR]

39:30.993 --> 39:32.160
JUST A MOMENT, PLEASE.

39:32.328 --> 39:33.912
COME IN.

39:34.080 --> 39:35.914
NO, NO, OF COURSE NOT,
MR. O'HARA.

39:36.082 --> 39:38.541
I DON'T WANT TO ALARM YOU
UNDULY, BUT THERE'S STILL

39:38.709 --> 39:40.126
NO WORD OF BERNADETTE.

39:40.294 --> 39:41.774
ARE YOU SURE YOU
HAVE NO INKLING WHERE

39:41.921 --> 39:44.464
SHE COULD POSSIBLY BE?

39:44.632 --> 39:47.092
YES, MR. O'HARA, OF
COURSE I REALIZE SHE IS MY

39:47.259 --> 39:50.637
RESPONSIBILITY ALSO.

39:51.222 --> 39:52.472
CERTAINLY.

39:52.640 --> 39:54.057
I WILL CALL YOU TOMORROW.

39:54.225 --> 39:56.684
BYE.

39:57.269 --> 40:01.314
WELL, MISS WAINWRIGHT, I
HAVE TO TELL YOU THAT I DO NOT

40:01.482 --> 40:04.526
FOR ONE MOMENT BELIEVE THAT TWO
OF THE TOP TEN COULD DISAPPEAR

40:04.693 --> 40:06.903
WITHOUT THE REST OF YOU
BEING IN ON THE JOKE.

40:07.071 --> 40:12.200
BUT, MRS. PATTERSON, REALLY,
I HAVE NO IDEA WHERE THEY ARE.

40:12.868 --> 40:14.508
VIRGINIA, I KNOW THAT
IN SOME WAYS YOU ARE

40:14.662 --> 40:15.912
A SPECIAL CASE.

40:16.080 --> 40:18.998
IT MUST HAVE BEEN HARD FOR
YOU TO COME BACK TO CRAWFORD.

40:19.166 --> 40:21.251
I KNEW YOUR
MOTHER, YOU KNOW.

40:21.419 --> 40:24.838
WELL, AFTER ALL,
SHE WAS A LOCAL GIRL.

40:25.005 --> 40:28.967
VIRGINIA, YOUR FATHER
IS A VERY WEALTHY MAN,

40:29.135 --> 40:31.970
AND I'M AFRAID THAT IS THE
BEGINNING OF THE TROUBLE.

40:32.138 --> 40:36.015
YOU AND ALL YOUR GANG... YOU
THINK THAT BECAUSE YOU ARE RICH

40:36.183 --> 40:39.310
YOU CAN SNEER AT PEOPLE WHO
HAVE HAD TO WORK HARD, PEOPLE

40:39.478 --> 40:42.772
WHO HAVE HAD TO FIGHT TO GET A
DECENT EDUCATION, THAT YOU CAN

40:42.940 --> 40:44.941
DO JUST AS YOU PLEASE.

40:45.109 --> 40:47.402
WELL, I'M AFRAID IT DOESN'T
WORK LIKE THAT... AT LEAST NOT

40:47.570 --> 40:50.071
AT CRAWFORD ACADEMY.

40:50.239 --> 40:53.616
FOR NOW, I'M GOING TO ASSIGN
YOU TO AFTER-SCHOOL DUTIES.

40:53.784 --> 40:57.036
PLEASE REPORT TO
MR. MUNCIE AT 3:00.

40:57.204 --> 40:58.913
WE'LL SEE IF A LITTLE
DETENTION DOESN'T

40:59.081 --> 41:00.582
JAR YOUR MEMORY.

41:00.749 --> 41:03.209
[BUZZER]

41:03.878 --> 41:05.587
YES, MILLIE, WHAT IS IT?

41:05.754 --> 41:07.380
AMBASSADOR VERCOURS
ON LINE 1.

41:07.548 --> 41:10.133
IT'S ABOUT ETIENNE.

41:16.807 --> 41:20.393
BONJOUR,
MONSIEUR L'AMBASSADEUR!

41:21.437 --> 41:23.354
ANN: SO, DID SHE GIVE
YOU THE SAME HORSE SHIT?

41:23.522 --> 41:24.647
WHAT A BITCH.

41:24.815 --> 41:26.274
HOW ARE WE SUPPOSED TO
KNOW WHERE EVERYBODY IS?

41:26.442 --> 41:28.735
AND WHAT THEY'RE UP TO.

41:28.903 --> 41:30.987
WELL, I ALREADY
KNOW WHAT THEY'RE UP TO.

41:31.155 --> 41:33.615
IT'S JUST WHERE
THAT HAS ME STUMPED.

41:33.782 --> 41:35.116
I JUST HOPE
THEY'RE ALL RIGHT.

41:35.284 --> 41:37.994
IT IS KIND OF WEIRD
VANISHING LIKE THAT.

41:38.162 --> 41:39.704
YEAH, I KNOW.

41:39.872 --> 41:41.414
YOU WANT TO GO TO
THE MOVIES TONIGHT?

41:41.582 --> 41:43.166
THE FILM SOCIETY'S
SHOWING "HIGH NOON."

41:43.334 --> 41:45.293
SOUNDS GREAT.

41:45.461 --> 41:47.504
I LOVE GARY COOPER.

41:47.671 --> 41:50.465
[INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS]

41:50.633 --> 41:52.467
ANN: AH, I AGREE.

41:52.635 --> 41:56.095
ALFRED: BUT ZINNEMANN...
ZINNEMANN IS SO FABULOUS!

41:56.263 --> 41:57.639
STEVE: EVERY TIME I GO SEE
A WESTERN, THEY PUT GREASE

41:57.806 --> 41:58.806
IN THEIR HAIR.

41:58.974 --> 42:00.016
HI, RUDI.

42:00.184 --> 42:01.344
HEY, YOU MISSED
A GREAT MOVIE.

42:01.352 --> 42:02.352
YEAH?

42:02.520 --> 42:04.760
SEEMS LIKE SOMEONE DIDN'T
BOTHER TO ASK ME TO COME ALONG.

42:04.897 --> 42:06.356
COME ON, STEVE, LET'S GO.

42:06.524 --> 42:07.732
MAGGIE, I WANT TO HAVE A
WORD WITH YOU FOR A MINUTE,

42:07.900 --> 42:09.025
OKAY?

42:09.193 --> 42:10.527
STEVE, GET OUT
OF THE WAY, OKAY?

42:10.694 --> 42:12.737
I SAID GET OUT OF THE WAY!

42:12.905 --> 42:15.031
RUDI, COME ON!

42:15.199 --> 42:17.909
COME ON, LIGHTEN UP!

42:18.077 --> 42:20.036
YOU TOUCH ME AGAIN,
I'M GONNA FUCKIN' KILL YOU!

42:20.204 --> 42:22.539
HEY, COME ON.

42:22.706 --> 42:25.416
LET'S ALL GO
HAVE A DRINK, OKAY?

42:25.584 --> 42:28.294
LOOK, WHY DON'T YOU
GUYS JUST GO TO FUCKIN' HELL?

42:29.797 --> 42:32.549
[ENGINE TURNS OVER]

42:33.050 --> 42:35.426
LET'S GO, MAGGIE.

42:40.057 --> 42:42.016
WE'RE ALL FALLING APART.

42:42.184 --> 42:44.477
COME ON, I'LL TAKE YOU HOME.

42:47.064 --> 42:50.149
NOW, ALFRED, YOU
CAN BY ME THAT DRINK.

42:50.317 --> 42:52.777
COME ON, ANN.

43:01.579 --> 43:09.579
♪♪♪

43:36.447 --> 43:39.449
AMELIA?

43:46.123 --> 43:48.583
OH, IT'S YOU.

44:00.721 --> 44:02.639
AMELIA'S COMING
OVER WITH SOME STUFF.

44:02.806 --> 44:05.808
SHE SHOULD BE
HERE ANY SECOND.

44:05.976 --> 44:07.268
HEY, DO ME A FAVOR.

44:07.436 --> 44:09.354
SLAP ON 10 MORE, HUH?

44:09.521 --> 44:12.023
[SIGHS]

44:12.191 --> 44:15.777
I GUESS I SHOULD HAVE MINDED
MY OWN BUSINESS TONIGHT, HUH?

44:21.617 --> 44:24.494
AMELIA SAYS WE'RE FALLIN'
APART, AND I'M STARTIN'

44:24.662 --> 44:28.498
TO AGREE WITH HER.

44:45.557 --> 44:47.433
THAT WAS KIND OF EASY.

44:47.601 --> 44:50.520
HOW ABOUT TWO MORE 25s?

44:52.439 --> 44:53.981
I JUST DON'T UNDERSTAND IT.

44:54.149 --> 44:57.527
WE'VE BEEN TOGETHER FOR SUCH
A LONG TIME, AND ALL OF THE

44:57.695 --> 45:00.905
SUDDEN WE'RE AT
EACH OTHER'S THROATS.

45:04.743 --> 45:07.662
MAKE SURE YOU
TIGHTEN IT, HUH?

45:18.549 --> 45:23.845
[PANTING]

45:26.473 --> 45:29.434
OKAY, THAT'S IT.

45:30.436 --> 45:31.894
WHAT ARE YOU DOIN'?!

45:32.062 --> 45:34.355
COME ON, PUT 'EM BACK.

45:34.523 --> 45:37.775
COME ON, QUIT
SCREWIN' AROUND!

45:38.444 --> 45:40.278
COME ON,
PLEASE PUT 'EM BACK!

45:40.446 --> 45:44.115
FOR GOD'S FUCKIN'
SAKE, PUT 'EM BACK!

45:45.033 --> 45:48.911
GOD, PLEASE.

45:52.040 --> 45:54.333
I-I C-C-CAN'T...
CAN'T HOLD IT.

45:54.501 --> 45:55.793
IT'S NOT A JOKE ANYMORE.

45:55.961 --> 45:58.045
PLEASE.

45:58.213 --> 46:00.131
I CAN'T... I CAN'T HOLD IT.

46:00.299 --> 46:02.341
AAAH!

46:02.509 --> 46:04.969
[GURGLING]

46:20.027 --> 46:21.235
HEY, GREG!

46:21.403 --> 46:22.528
PIZZA DELIVERY GIRL.

46:22.696 --> 46:25.490
I'VE GOT ONE ALL
DRESSED WITH ANCHOVIES.

46:27.034 --> 46:35.034
♪♪♪

46:37.002 --> 46:40.004
GREG.

46:41.173 --> 46:44.592
GREG?

46:45.427 --> 46:47.804
AAAH!

46:48.347 --> 46:48.638
[CROWD CHEERING
AND APPLAUDING]

46:48.806 --> 46:50.181
VIRGINIA: KILL 'EM!

46:50.349 --> 46:51.808
KILL 'EM!

46:51.975 --> 46:55.186
KILL, KILL, KILL 'EM!

46:55.354 --> 46:57.522
KILL 'EM!

46:57.689 --> 46:59.816
[CROWD CHEERING]

46:59.983 --> 47:04.362
GO, RUDI, RUDI!

47:09.701 --> 47:13.037
[WHISTLE BLOWS]

47:30.764 --> 47:34.141
CHEERLEADERS: [CHANTING]
CRAWFORD COULD... FOR RUDI!

47:34.309 --> 47:36.435
TWO TO TEN SAYS
WE'LL NEVER MAKE IT.

47:36.603 --> 47:37.979
YOU GOT IT.

47:38.146 --> 47:40.022
[WHISTLE BLOWS]

47:40.190 --> 47:43.609
COME ON, GUYS,
WE'RE RUNNING OUT OF TIME.

47:43.861 --> 47:45.236
YOUNG MAN: THIS WAY!

47:45.404 --> 47:46.529
I GOT IT!

47:46.697 --> 47:47.947
[WHISTLE BLOWS]

47:48.115 --> 47:49.115
[CROWD GROANS]

47:49.157 --> 47:50.658
OH, GOD.

47:51.118 --> 47:52.159
OH, GOD.

47:52.327 --> 47:54.745
OH, GIVE ME A BREAK.

47:55.205 --> 47:57.206
HEY, DON'T WORRY.

47:57.374 --> 47:59.000
GREG WOULDN'T TAKE OFF
IN THE MIDDLE OF THE NIGHT

47:59.167 --> 48:01.294
WITHOUT TELLING ME.

48:02.254 --> 48:03.713
WE SURE COULD USE HIM NOW.

48:03.881 --> 48:06.674
[DRUMROLL]

48:07.134 --> 48:09.135
[WHISTLE BLOWS]

48:09.303 --> 48:12.513
[CROWD CHEERING]

48:13.807 --> 48:16.767
ALL RIGHT!

48:19.646 --> 48:21.939
CHEERLEADERS:
...AND ROLL THE DICE...

48:22.107 --> 48:27.278
ACES HIGH, DEUCES LOW,
COME ON, CRAWFORD, LET'S GO!

48:27.446 --> 48:29.780
GIVE ME ONE MORE!

48:35.996 --> 48:38.664
COME ON, BABY!

48:39.082 --> 48:41.667
COME ON, RUDI, COME ON!

48:45.088 --> 48:47.757
NO, NO, NO, NO, NOT NOW!

48:50.260 --> 48:52.011
[WHISTLE BLOWS]

48:53.639 --> 49:01.639
♪♪♪

49:11.073 --> 49:13.991
[SMOOCHES, LAUGHS]

49:15.410 --> 49:17.912
THAT'S FIVE... ONE MORE.

49:18.080 --> 49:19.914
COME ON.

49:20.082 --> 49:22.833
THANK YOU.

49:24.127 --> 49:25.670
VIRGINIA: OH, RUDI,
YOU WERE GREAT!

49:25.837 --> 49:27.588
THAT GOAL WAS JUST TERRIFIC!

49:27.756 --> 49:30.758
YEAH, SORRY I WAS, UH,
SUCH A JERK LAST NIGHT.

49:30.926 --> 49:32.343
AW, THAT'S OKAY.

49:32.511 --> 49:36.180
HEY, ARE YOU, UH, DOING
ANYTHING LATER ON?

49:36.348 --> 49:37.515
NO.

49:37.683 --> 49:40.101
WELL, I'LL MEET
YOU AT THE CHAPEL.

49:40.268 --> 49:43.229
OKAY.

49:47.150 --> 49:55.150
♪♪♪

50:02.249 --> 50:04.917
RUDI: [GHOULISH VOICE]
YOU CANNOT REFUSE.

50:05.085 --> 50:10.006
YOU MUST FOLLOW
ME INTO THE TOWER.

50:10.590 --> 50:18.590
♪♪♪

50:38.702 --> 50:43.456
AH, THAT SMELL... THE
PUTRESCENCE OF DECAY.

50:43.623 --> 50:45.663
BUT FEAR NOT, MY LITTLE
DARLING, FOR ALTHOUGH WE ARE

50:45.751 --> 50:49.754
DOOMED TO DIE, WE SHALL
LIVE FOREVER IN THE RANKS

50:49.921 --> 50:52.214
OF THE UNDEAD.

50:52.382 --> 50:53.799
RUDI, YOU STOP THAT
RIGHT NOW OR I'M NOT GONNA

50:53.967 --> 50:56.343
GO ANOTHER STEP.

50:57.971 --> 50:59.847
I'M SORRY.

51:00.015 --> 51:02.600
I CAN'T RESIST IN
A PLACE LIKE THIS.

51:02.768 --> 51:06.270
YEAH, IT'S... IT'S
CREEPY ALL RIGHT.

51:37.844 --> 51:40.137
YOU'VE, UH, NEVER BEEN
UP HERE BEFORE, HAVE YOU?

51:40.305 --> 51:42.306
YOU KNOW, I-I KEEP ON
FORGETTING THAT YOU'RE

51:42.474 --> 51:44.058
NEW HERE AT CRAWFORD.

51:44.226 --> 51:45.392
NO, I'M NOT.

51:45.560 --> 51:46.769
I WAS HERE BEFORE YOU.

51:46.937 --> 51:48.270
OH, YEAH?

51:48.438 --> 51:49.772
WHEN?

51:49.940 --> 51:52.483
FOUR YEARS AGO.

51:52.651 --> 51:53.692
THAT'S FUNNY.

51:53.860 --> 51:57.029
HOW COME, UH,
NOBODY EVER MENTIONED IT?

51:57.197 --> 51:59.698
WELL, IT WAS JUST
FOR A FEW WEEKS, BUT...

51:59.866 --> 52:03.786
THEY'VE ALL FORGOTTEN ME.

52:04.746 --> 52:06.372
[IMITATING QUASIMODO]

52:06.540 --> 52:09.917
I WILL NEVER FORGET YOU,
MY DARLING.

52:10.627 --> 52:12.545
RUDI!

52:12.712 --> 52:13.963
WOW!

52:14.131 --> 52:15.172
I-I JUST LOVE THIS PLACE!

52:15.340 --> 52:16.465
I SWEAR!

52:16.633 --> 52:19.426
I FEEL JUST LIKE QUASIMODO...
QUASIMODO IN A BELL TOWER!

52:19.594 --> 52:21.971
THANK GOD YOU
DON'T LOOK LIKE HIM.

52:25.934 --> 52:27.685
[IMITATING QUASIMODO]

52:27.853 --> 52:30.855
GIVE ME A LITTLE KISS,
ESMERALDA... A LITTLE PECK

52:31.022 --> 52:32.815
ON THE CHEEK.

52:32.983 --> 52:34.233
RUDI, STOP IT.

52:34.401 --> 52:35.568
STOP IT!

52:35.735 --> 52:38.279
NEXT THING I KNOW, YOU'LL
BE SWINGING FROM THE BELL ROPE.

52:38.446 --> 52:40.030
HEY, THAT'S NOT A BAD IDEA!

52:40.198 --> 52:43.200
RUDI, ARE YOU CRAZY?!

52:45.245 --> 52:46.954
[GROANS]

52:47.122 --> 52:51.000
VIRGINIA...

52:51.168 --> 52:56.380
YOU KNOW, I... IF I CUT
THIS BELL ROPE ALMOST

52:56.548 --> 52:59.884
ALL THE WAY THROUGH...

53:01.928 --> 53:04.638
NO.

53:04.806 --> 53:08.893
RUDI, NO.

53:11.897 --> 53:14.481
VIRGINIA...

53:15.483 --> 53:18.527
I'VE GOT A KNIFE.

53:24.701 --> 53:27.536
VIRGINIA...

53:27.704 --> 53:30.289
DON'T GO AWAY.

53:32.167 --> 53:35.586
COME OVER HERE, VIRGINIA.

53:45.138 --> 53:53.138
♪♪♪

53:58.526 --> 54:02.196
[PANTING]

54:02.364 --> 54:10.364
♪♪♪

54:36.773 --> 54:39.525
[BELL TOLLS]

54:40.318 --> 54:43.404
JESUS.

55:01.381 --> 55:03.173
HELP.

55:03.341 --> 55:05.968
MURDER!

55:09.806 --> 55:11.140
IS DR. FARADAY
IN HIS OFFICE?

55:11.308 --> 55:12.433
PROBABLY.

55:12.600 --> 55:15.352
LET ME CHECK FOR YOU.

55:24.904 --> 55:27.865
[EERIE MUSIC PLAYS]

55:28.033 --> 55:31.076
[MONITOR BEEPING]

55:31.244 --> 55:35.289
[HEARTBEATS]

55:44.841 --> 55:49.094
MAN: ROLL FOR THE FLAP.

55:49.262 --> 55:50.679
FISH HOOK.

55:50.847 --> 55:52.765
DRILL IS NEXT.

55:52.932 --> 55:54.892
IRRIGATION, PLEASE.

56:04.444 --> 56:07.404
FREE BONE FLAP.

56:07.906 --> 56:09.239
HER VITAL SIGNS STABLE?

56:09.407 --> 56:11.327
YES, SHE'S BREATHING WELL,
AND HER BLOOD PRESSURE

56:11.409 --> 56:13.285
IS STABLE.

56:13.453 --> 56:14.745
BRAIN IS SWELLING.

56:14.913 --> 56:17.706
I'LL HYPERVENTILATE HER.

56:17.874 --> 56:19.333
[ALARM BEEPING]

56:19.501 --> 56:20.542
CEREBRAL EDEMA...
SHE'S FINISHED.

56:20.710 --> 56:23.003
CLOSE HER UP.

56:23.838 --> 56:26.882
[CRYING]

56:27.342 --> 56:28.509
NOW, CLOSE HER!

56:28.676 --> 56:29.301
SHE'S DEAD!

56:29.469 --> 56:33.931
OH, JESUS, NO!
SOMEBODY STOP HIM!

56:35.558 --> 56:39.520
GOD, DON'T LET HIM DO IT!
SOMEBODY HELP ME!

56:51.199 --> 56:55.619
HE KILLED PART OF MY BRAIN.
HE KILLED PART OF ME!

56:56.496 --> 56:59.706
VIRGINIA, YOU'VE REMEMBERED
THE OPERATION.

56:59.874 --> 57:02.960
IT'S COMING BACK
PIECE BY PIECE.

57:03.128 --> 57:05.295
THE KNIFE...

57:05.463 --> 57:07.840
THE... T-THE BLOOD...

57:08.007 --> 57:09.842
THE OPERATION, VIRGINIA.

57:10.009 --> 57:11.468
NO!
IT WAS TODAY!

57:11.636 --> 57:13.762
IT WAS TODAY!
DON'T YOU SEE?!

57:13.930 --> 57:15.848
I WAS WITH RUDI!

57:16.015 --> 57:19.435
WE WERE IN THE BELL
TOWER, AND HE HAD A KNIFE!

57:19.602 --> 57:22.271
I WAS SO SCARED!

57:22.439 --> 57:24.314
AND THEN WHAT HAPPENED?

57:24.482 --> 57:27.693
I DON'T KNOW!
I-I PANICKED!

57:27.861 --> 57:29.111
I-I CAME HERE.

57:29.279 --> 57:35.159
GOD, I THOUGHT
YOU'D HELP ME!

57:35.326 --> 57:39.913
[SOBBING]

57:40.957 --> 57:43.292
COME HERE.
COME WITH ME.

57:43.460 --> 57:44.668
COME ON.
YOU NEED SOME REST.

57:44.711 --> 57:47.796
I'M GONNA TAKE YOU HOME.
ALL RIGHT?

57:47.964 --> 57:50.549
[SOBBING]

57:50.717 --> 57:54.803
LISTEN, I'LL, UH, I'LL CHECK
OUT THE BELL TOWER.

57:54.971 --> 57:57.639
DON'T YOU WORRY
ABOUT A THING.

57:57.807 --> 58:00.559
RIGHT NOW I'M
TAKING YOU HOME.

58:00.727 --> 58:02.561
COME ON.
COME ON.

58:02.729 --> 58:07.149
IT'S ALL RIGHT.
IT'S ALL RIGHT.

58:07.317 --> 58:10.402
[BICYCLE BELL DINGS]

58:12.322 --> 58:20.322
♪♪♪

58:28.046 --> 58:30.255
MAN: ...THAT TWO MORE
STUDENTS HAVE DISAPPEARED.

58:30.423 --> 58:33.509
LIEUTENANT REESE REFUSES
TO CONFIRM OR DENY THAT POLICE

58:33.676 --> 58:35.427
BELIEVE THE INCIDENTS
ARE RELATED.

58:35.595 --> 58:37.930
ALSO MISSING IS
ETIENNE VERCOURS,

58:38.097 --> 58:40.140
A FRENCH CITIZEN ON
AN EXCHANGE PROGRAM

58:40.308 --> 58:41.600
AT THE CRAWFORD ACADEMY.

58:41.768 --> 58:44.520
HE IS THE SON OF AMBASSADOR
ADRIENNE VERCOURS.

58:44.687 --> 58:47.105
THE THIRD MISSING STUDENT IS
GREGORY HELLMAN, THE SON

58:47.273 --> 58:49.775
OF NATHANIEL HELLMAN,
CHAIRMAN OF THE TRANS-ALLIED

58:49.943 --> 58:51.527
FINANCE CORPORATION.

58:51.694 --> 58:54.238
IN OTHER NEWS, POLICE ARE
INVESTIGATING A MYSTERIOUS

58:54.405 --> 58:57.032
INCIDENT AT CRAWFORD
CHAPEL YESTERDAY.

58:57.200 --> 58:59.243
VANDALS SEVERED
THE BELL-TOWER ROPE.

58:59.410 --> 59:01.912
BUT WITH THE DISCOVERY OF
A BLOODIED KNIFE, POLICE ARE

59:02.080 --> 59:04.623
LOOKING FURTHER INTO THE
MATTER, BELIEVING FOUL PLAY

59:04.791 --> 59:06.625
MAY BE INVOLVED AS WELL.

59:06.793 --> 59:09.503
IN SPORTS, THE 5-GAME
UNBEATEN STREAK OF THE HOUS...

59:09.671 --> 59:12.130
[RADIO SHUTS OFF]

59:19.305 --> 59:21.223
YOUNG MAN: YES, SIR,
THEY'RE IN THE LIBRARY.

59:21.391 --> 59:23.058
MAN: WHEN DID YOU
LAST SEE GREG HELLMAN?

59:23.226 --> 59:25.102
AMELIA: I SAW HIM
THE NIGHT BEFORE LAST.

59:25.270 --> 59:27.854
WE WENT TO
THE SHOW TOGETHER.

59:28.022 --> 59:30.190
JUST GIVE ME A NAME,
RANK, AND SERIAL NUMBER.

59:30.358 --> 59:31.650
IT WAS AN ANONYMOUS
PHONE CALL.

59:31.818 --> 59:32.985
THAT'S WHY THEY'RE DIGGING.

59:33.152 --> 59:35.195
CHRIST, EVERY DAY
SOMEONE ELSE IS MISSING.

59:35.363 --> 59:36.530
WHERE THE HELL IS RUDI?

59:36.698 --> 59:37.739
WHY ARE YOU WORRIED?

59:37.907 --> 59:40.534
STEVE: THE OTHER NIGHT,
YOU WANTED TO KILL HIM.

59:42.870 --> 59:44.413
[SOBS]

59:44.581 --> 59:46.707
THEY THINK THAT
GREG MAY BE DEAD.

59:46.874 --> 59:50.085
[SOBBING]

59:55.800 --> 59:57.509
MAN: OKAY, THAT'S ALL.

59:57.677 --> 59:58.677
DAVID.

59:58.803 --> 59:59.803
VIRGINIA, COME HERE.

59:59.971 --> 01:00:01.179
I WANT TO TALK TO YOU.

01:00:01.347 --> 01:00:02.347
DAVID, I'M SO SCARED.

01:00:02.473 --> 01:00:03.640
RUDI IS MISSING.

01:00:03.808 --> 01:00:05.809
NOW, LISTEN, IT'S VERY
IMPORTANT THAT YOU TELL ME

01:00:05.977 --> 01:00:09.980
EXACTLY WHAT HAPPENED IN
THE BELL CHAPEL YESTERDAY.

01:00:11.107 --> 01:00:12.482
WELL, I WENT WITH RUDI.

01:00:12.650 --> 01:00:13.817
WE WENT UP TO THE CHURCH.

01:00:13.985 --> 01:00:16.653
DR. FARADAY, IS ANYTHING
THE MATTER?

01:00:17.447 --> 01:00:18.447
[INDISTINCT TALKING]

01:00:18.615 --> 01:00:21.158
YOU'D BETTER COME OUTSIDE.

01:00:21.743 --> 01:00:24.911
HEY, EVERYBODY, I THINK
THEY FOUND SOMETHING OUTSIDE!

01:00:25.079 --> 01:00:28.624
[INDISTINCT SHOUTING]

01:00:35.965 --> 01:00:39.551
[INDISTINCT TALKING]

01:00:42.805 --> 01:00:45.349
PLEASE, LET ME THROUGH!

01:00:51.147 --> 01:00:52.856
BACK.

01:00:53.024 --> 01:00:56.234
LET'S MOVE IT ON BACK.

01:01:02.492 --> 01:01:05.410
[GASPS]

01:01:13.586 --> 01:01:14.920
AAAH!

01:01:15.088 --> 01:01:16.129
HI, THERE.

01:01:16.297 --> 01:01:17.297
RUDI!

01:01:17.382 --> 01:01:18.382
WHERE HAVE YOU BEEN?!

01:01:18.549 --> 01:01:19.549
WHERE HAVE I BEEN?
WHERE HAVE YOU BEEN?

01:01:19.717 --> 01:01:21.468
WHAT HAPPENED
TO YOU YESTERDAY?

01:01:21.636 --> 01:01:22.719
YESTERDAY?

01:01:22.887 --> 01:01:24.096
IN THE BELL TOWER!

01:01:24.263 --> 01:01:25.597
I NEARLY CUT MY HAND
OFF WITH THAT LOUSY ROPE!

01:01:25.765 --> 01:01:28.558
15 STITCHES!

01:01:29.227 --> 01:01:32.312
YOU... YOU CREEP!

01:01:32.480 --> 01:01:35.399
YOU HAD ME BELIEVING... IT WAS ALL A JOKE.

01:01:35.566 --> 01:01:37.401
Y-YOU DIDN'T TELL
ANYBODY, DID YOU?

01:01:37.568 --> 01:01:38.777
TELL ANYBODY?!

01:01:38.945 --> 01:01:40.404
THEY'VE BEEN TURNING THE
SCHOOL UPSIDE-DOWN LOOKING FOR

01:01:40.571 --> 01:01:41.655
YOU AND THE OTHERS!

01:01:41.823 --> 01:01:43.365
THEY'RE EVEN OUT THERE RIGHT
NOW DIGGING IN THE GARDEN!

01:01:43.533 --> 01:01:46.159
I WAS AFRAID
TO SAY ANYTHING.

01:02:01.092 --> 01:02:04.094
OH, DEAR GOD.

01:02:10.518 --> 01:02:13.729
UH, LIEUTENANT, DO YOU
MIND IF I TAKE A LOOK AT THAT?

01:02:13.896 --> 01:02:15.564
GO RIGHT AHEAD, DR. FARADAY.

01:02:15.732 --> 01:02:17.691
THANK YOU.

01:02:18.359 --> 01:02:26.359
♪♪♪

01:02:30.329 --> 01:02:33.415
NOW, I THINK YOU SHOULD
HAVE ANOTHER LOOK AT THIS.

01:02:34.167 --> 01:02:40.046
UH, PROPERTY OF CRAWFORD
ACADEMY SCIENCE DEPARTMENT.

01:02:40.465 --> 01:02:43.300
[LAUGHTER]

01:02:44.510 --> 01:02:45.635
[CHUCKLES]

01:02:45.803 --> 01:02:47.929
HERE.

01:02:50.308 --> 01:02:53.018
RUDI.

01:02:55.605 --> 01:02:57.689
VIRGINIA.

01:02:58.775 --> 01:03:00.650
RUDI, I THOUGHT
THAT WAS YOU.

01:03:00.818 --> 01:03:02.736
I'M PRETTIER THAN THAT.

01:03:12.079 --> 01:03:14.331
YOU'RE STILL A BASTARD.

01:03:14.499 --> 01:03:15.957
LISTEN, DAVID, PLEASE DON'T
SAY ANYTHING ABOUT THIS

01:03:16.125 --> 01:03:17.375
TO ANYBODY.

01:03:17.543 --> 01:03:18.960
I DON'T WANT TO
GET RUDI IN TROUBLE.

01:03:19.128 --> 01:03:21.046
NO, I'M NOT GONNA
SAY ANYTHING TO ANYBODY.

01:03:21.214 --> 01:03:26.968
BUT I-I MUST ADMIT, SOME
OF YOUR FRIENDS HAVE

01:03:27.136 --> 01:03:29.095
A MACABRE SENSE OF HUMOR.

01:03:29.263 --> 01:03:30.722
I JUST HOPE THESE
KIDS AREN'T HAVING

01:03:30.890 --> 01:03:33.642
AN ADVERSE EFFECT ON YOU.

01:03:34.310 --> 01:03:36.144
THEY'RE NOT.

01:03:36.312 --> 01:03:37.521
[SIGHS]

01:03:37.688 --> 01:03:41.191
LISTEN, UH... MY BIRTHDAY'S
SUNDAY, AND, UH, I'D LIKE

01:03:41.359 --> 01:03:43.318
TO INVITE YOU TO DINNER.

01:03:43.486 --> 01:03:45.278
WHY, I'D BE DELIGHTED.

01:03:45.446 --> 01:03:46.988
ANN: VIRGINIA!

01:03:47.156 --> 01:03:48.865
OH, I GOT TO RUN.

01:03:49.033 --> 01:03:51.284
THANKS, DAVID.

01:03:53.996 --> 01:03:55.956
COME ON, LET'S GO.

01:03:56.123 --> 01:03:58.917
[LAUGHTER]

01:03:59.085 --> 01:04:01.878
[INDISTINCT TALKING]

01:04:05.132 --> 01:04:08.176
AND MAGGIE... I THOUGHT SHE
WAS GONNA TEAR YOUR BALLS OFF

01:04:08.344 --> 01:04:10.846
AFTER SHE GOT OVER
THAT JOYOUS REUNION.

01:04:11.013 --> 01:04:13.223
WELL, IT ALL WORKED OUT
FOR THE BEST.

01:04:13.391 --> 01:04:17.060
NOW I CAN TAKE VIRGINIA TO
THE DANCE, CAN'T I, SWEETHEART?

01:04:17.854 --> 01:04:20.313
BY THE WAY, WHERE'S ALFRED?

01:04:20.481 --> 01:04:21.648
[SIGHS]

01:04:21.816 --> 01:04:23.024
GOD, NOT ALFRED TOO.

01:04:23.192 --> 01:04:24.484
STEVE: MAYBE WE SHOULD ALL
PUT IN 20 BUCKS AND THE LAST

01:04:24.652 --> 01:04:26.152
ONE LEFT TAKES ALL.

01:04:26.320 --> 01:04:27.946
[LAUGHING]

01:04:28.114 --> 01:04:31.241
NO, YOU SEE, ALFRED IS
NOT A DISAPPEARER,

01:04:31.409 --> 01:04:33.451
HE'S A DISAPPEAREE.

01:04:33.619 --> 01:04:35.412
A DISAPPEAREE?

01:04:35.580 --> 01:04:37.998
I CAN JUST SEE HIM WALKING
THROUGH THE WOODS

01:04:38.165 --> 01:04:40.041
STALKING OUT HIS LATEST VICTIM.

01:04:40.209 --> 01:04:41.668
AH, GET SERIOUS, YOU GUYS!

01:04:41.836 --> 01:04:44.546
I HAVEN'T SEEN HIM
SINCE THIS MORNING.

01:04:44.714 --> 01:04:46.131
YEAH, NOR HAVE I.

01:04:46.299 --> 01:04:47.549
HOW 'BOUT YOU, GINNIE?

01:04:47.717 --> 01:04:50.468
HAVE YOU SEEN THE
PHANTOM TAXIDERMIST?

01:05:00.354 --> 01:05:02.230
ANN: VIRGINIA?

01:05:04.942 --> 01:05:07.903
VIRGINIA?

01:05:09.113 --> 01:05:17.113
♪♪♪

01:05:33.054 --> 01:05:36.014
VIRGINIA!

01:05:37.975 --> 01:05:45.975
♪♪♪

01:05:48.945 --> 01:05:56.945
♪♪♪

01:06:16.722 --> 01:06:19.724
[GATE CLOSES]

01:06:32.321 --> 01:06:40.321
♪♪♪

01:09:19.822 --> 01:09:23.992
[TELEPHONE RINGING]

01:09:29.832 --> 01:09:32.584
YEAH, I'M WATCHING
IT RIGHT NOW.

01:09:32.751 --> 01:09:35.377
LOOK, RED AND HIS CREW ARE
ON THEIR WAY UP FROM HOUSTON.

01:09:35.546 --> 01:09:37.666
I EXPECT YOU TO GIVE THEM ALL
THE COOPERATION YOU CAN,

01:09:37.715 --> 01:09:39.465
IS THAT CLEAR?

01:09:39.633 --> 01:09:40.925
ALL RIGHT.

01:09:41.093 --> 01:09:43.094
I'LL BE IN CALGARY IN
APPROXIMATELY FOUR HOURS.

01:09:43.261 --> 01:09:44.636
A JET'S STANDING BY.

01:09:44.805 --> 01:09:46.680
I WANT A CHOPPER
AT THE OTHER END.

01:09:46.849 --> 01:09:48.600
THANK YOU.

01:09:48.767 --> 01:09:51.394
[TELEPHONE RECEIVER CLICKS]

01:09:52.438 --> 01:09:55.190
HOW LONG WILL
YOU BE GONE, DADDY?

01:09:55.900 --> 01:09:57.150
IT'S HARD TO SAY, HONEY.

01:09:57.318 --> 01:10:00.028
AS LONG AS IT TAKES TO
GET THE DAMN THING OUT.

01:10:00.821 --> 01:10:02.906
WHAT ABOUT SUNDAY?

01:10:03.073 --> 01:10:05.116
SUNDAY?

01:10:08.412 --> 01:10:11.206
YOUR BIRTHDAY.

01:10:11.373 --> 01:10:13.917
[BRIEFCASE LATCHES CLICK]

01:10:19.840 --> 01:10:24.010
HEY, GLUMMY FACE,
LOOK... I'LL BE BACK, GINNIE.

01:10:24.178 --> 01:10:25.887
I'LL BE BACK BY
SUNDAY AFTERNOON.

01:10:26.055 --> 01:10:27.680
I PROMISE.

01:10:27.848 --> 01:10:29.265
YOU REALLY PROMISE?

01:10:29.433 --> 01:10:31.184
I PROMISE, HONEY.

01:10:31.352 --> 01:10:34.395
I'LL TELL YOU WHAT, IF
YOU CAN FIND TIME IN YOUR BUSY

01:10:34.563 --> 01:10:38.107
SOCIAL SCHEDULE TO PUT ON SOME
FANCY DUDS, WE'LL GO OUT

01:10:38.275 --> 01:10:40.902
ON THE TOWN AND CELEBRATE... JUST
THE TWO OF US.

01:10:41.070 --> 01:10:42.779
AND YOU KNOW SOMETHING?

01:10:42.947 --> 01:10:46.908
YOUR OLD DAD WILL SHOW YOU
SOME OF HIS MOST INCREDIBLE,

01:10:47.076 --> 01:10:50.912
ASTONISHING, FANCY FOOTWORK.

01:10:51.080 --> 01:10:53.998
WHAT DO YOU SAY?

01:10:54.166 --> 01:10:56.125
- OKAY.
- OKAY.

01:10:57.378 --> 01:10:59.379
I GOT TO GO.

01:10:59.546 --> 01:11:00.797
YOU'LL BE ALL RIGHT
HERE ON YOUR OWN.

01:11:00.965 --> 01:11:02.840
WHY DON'T YOU CALL A FRIEND,
INVITE THEM OVER?

01:11:03.008 --> 01:11:05.551
OR I CAN... I CAN
ALWAYS CALL DAVID.

01:11:05.719 --> 01:11:07.303
RIGHT.

01:11:07.471 --> 01:11:10.056
SEE YOU SUNDAY.

01:11:16.689 --> 01:11:20.149
HAPPY BIRTHDAY.

01:11:20.317 --> 01:11:22.944
[FOOTSTEPS]

01:11:23.529 --> 01:11:25.363
[CAR DOOR CLOSES]

01:11:25.531 --> 01:11:28.491
[ENGINE TURNS OVER]

01:11:30.995 --> 01:11:38.995
♪♪♪

01:12:11.493 --> 01:12:12.577
HAVE YOU SEEN ALFRED?

01:12:12.745 --> 01:12:14.203
NO.

01:12:14.371 --> 01:12:16.164
FOUR DOWN, SIX TO GO.

01:12:16.332 --> 01:12:17.832
COME ON, RUDI,
IT'S NOT FUNNY.

01:12:18.000 --> 01:12:19.125
WHO'S LAUGHING?

01:12:19.293 --> 01:12:20.543
YOU KNOW THE COPS ARE
OUT THERE DRAGGING THE CANAL

01:12:20.711 --> 01:12:23.379
LOOKING FOR BODIES?

01:12:37.436 --> 01:12:39.896
[MUSIC STOPS]

01:12:42.649 --> 01:12:44.025
[LAUGHS]

01:12:44.193 --> 01:12:45.151
RUDI, YOU GOT
TO DO ME A FAVOR.

01:12:45.319 --> 01:12:46.319
WHAT?

01:12:46.403 --> 01:12:47.945
GO DANCE WITH MAGGIE.

01:12:48.113 --> 01:12:49.489
WHOSE IDEA IS THIS?

01:12:49.656 --> 01:12:51.866
HERS.
SHE'S DRIVING ME NUTS.

01:12:52.034 --> 01:12:53.785
WELL, UH...

01:12:53.952 --> 01:12:56.871
OH, IT'S FINE WITH ME, RUDI.

01:12:58.248 --> 01:13:06.248
♪♪♪

01:13:21.730 --> 01:13:23.147
I DON'T CARE WHO KNOWS IT.

01:13:23.315 --> 01:13:25.108
I'M SCARED.

01:13:25.275 --> 01:13:26.484
DON'T WORRY ABOUT IT.

01:13:26.652 --> 01:13:29.112
I'LL TAKE YOU HOME.

01:13:32.366 --> 01:13:33.950
LET'S GET OUT OF HERE.

01:13:34.118 --> 01:13:35.284
AREN'T YOU HAVIN'
A GOOD TIME?

01:13:35.452 --> 01:13:37.662
WELL, SURE, BUT, UH,
WE COULD BE HAVING

01:13:37.830 --> 01:13:39.288
AN EVEN BETTER TIME.

01:13:39.456 --> 01:13:40.832
OH, REALLY?

01:13:40.999 --> 01:13:42.417
HOW?

01:13:42.584 --> 01:13:45.837
WE COULD, UH, GO FOR
A DRIVE, HAVE A TOKE.

01:13:46.004 --> 01:13:47.255
JUST THE TWO OF US?

01:13:47.423 --> 01:13:48.881
[LAUGHS]

01:13:49.049 --> 01:13:50.967
JUST THE TWO OF US.

01:13:51.135 --> 01:13:52.552
[SIGHS]

01:13:52.719 --> 01:13:54.178
SHAME ON YOU, STEVE.

01:13:54.346 --> 01:13:56.973
WHAT WOULD MY FATHER SAY?

01:13:58.350 --> 01:14:01.602
LUCKILY, HE'S AWAY
FOR THE WEEKEND.

01:14:05.023 --> 01:14:08.234
I MAKE REAL GOOD
MIDNIGHT SNACKS.

01:14:08.402 --> 01:14:10.486
YOU HUNGRY?

01:14:10.654 --> 01:14:13.030
AM I HUNGRY!

01:14:13.657 --> 01:14:16.284
MEET YOU OUTSIDE.

01:14:28.005 --> 01:14:30.256
UH, ANN, WHAT TIME ARE
YOU COMING OVER TOMORROW?

01:14:30.424 --> 01:14:31.883
UH, ABOUT NOON, OKAY?

01:14:32.050 --> 01:14:33.217
SEE YA.

01:14:33.385 --> 01:14:34.385
WAIT.

01:14:34.428 --> 01:14:35.428
WHERE ARE YOU GOING?

01:14:35.554 --> 01:14:36.679
MY PLACE.

01:14:36.847 --> 01:14:37.889
WITH STEVE?!

01:14:38.056 --> 01:14:40.183
YEAH.

01:14:42.561 --> 01:14:50.561
♪♪♪

01:15:24.478 --> 01:15:27.605
MMM.
SMELLS GOOD.

01:15:33.111 --> 01:15:34.654
WHAT'S THAT?

01:15:34.821 --> 01:15:37.365
I'M MAKING YOURS
NICE AND SPICY.

01:15:37.533 --> 01:15:39.659
OH, I LIKE IT SPICY.

01:15:39.826 --> 01:15:41.327
GOOD.

01:15:41.495 --> 01:15:43.788
THANK YOU.

01:15:46.416 --> 01:15:48.334
MMM.

01:15:48.502 --> 01:15:50.836
DON'T YOU LIKE HOT THINGS?

01:15:51.004 --> 01:15:53.798
SOME HOT THINGS.

01:16:01.765 --> 01:16:04.225
GOD, AM I RIPPED.

01:16:23.745 --> 01:16:25.538
MY ASS IS BURNING.

01:16:25.706 --> 01:16:28.374
[LAUGHS]

01:16:31.670 --> 01:16:34.547
[LAUGHS]

01:16:46.143 --> 01:16:51.188
MMM.
DELICIOUS.

01:16:52.357 --> 01:16:55.735
WELL, HAVE SOME MORE.

01:17:01.158 --> 01:17:09.158
♪♪♪

01:17:14.630 --> 01:17:20.343
♪♪♪

01:17:43.241 --> 01:17:46.035
[HORN HONKS]

01:17:47.954 --> 01:17:50.831
[HONKING]

01:17:52.334 --> 01:17:55.044
[HONKING]

01:18:03.136 --> 01:18:04.637
WHAT TIME IS IT?

01:18:04.805 --> 01:18:05.971
PAST NOON!

01:18:06.139 --> 01:18:07.515
COME ON, IT'S
TIME TO GET UP!

01:18:07.683 --> 01:18:09.058
I WANT TO HEAR ALL THE
GORY DETAILS ABOUT YOU

01:18:09.226 --> 01:18:11.936
AND STEVE LAST NIGHT.

01:18:12.979 --> 01:18:15.481
LAST NIGHT?

01:18:16.024 --> 01:18:19.151
WHAT THE HELL
WAS LAST NIGHT?

01:18:20.112 --> 01:18:22.029
I DON'T REMEMBER ANYTHING.

01:18:22.197 --> 01:18:24.949
OH, BULLSHIT.

01:18:26.326 --> 01:18:27.993
JUST A MINUTE.

01:18:28.161 --> 01:18:30.621
I'LL BE RIGHT BACK.

01:18:36.461 --> 01:18:37.628
HERE ARE THE KEYS.
COME ON UP.

01:18:37.796 --> 01:18:39.422
I'M GONNA TAKE A SHOWER.

01:18:39.589 --> 01:18:40.881
OKAY.

01:18:41.049 --> 01:18:49.049
♪♪♪

01:19:08.702 --> 01:19:12.788
[CLACKING]

01:19:12.956 --> 01:19:17.376
[THUNDER]

01:19:21.089 --> 01:19:22.840
MOMMY, I-IT DOESN'T MATTER.

01:19:23.008 --> 01:19:25.426
NEVER... I'LL NEVER
FORGET THIS!

01:19:25.594 --> 01:19:27.678
THEY DON'T KNOW
HOW IT HURTS...

01:19:27.846 --> 01:19:30.139
BUT THEY'LL LEARN!

01:19:30.307 --> 01:19:32.391
BUT... BUT DADDY SAYS... NEVER
MIND WHAT DADDY SAYS!

01:19:32.559 --> 01:19:35.144
WHERE IS HE
WHEN WE NEED HIM?!

01:19:35.312 --> 01:19:37.313
BE CAREFUL!

01:19:37.481 --> 01:19:39.273
CRAZY SON OF A BITCH!

01:19:39.441 --> 01:19:41.108
[BELL CLANGING]

01:19:41.276 --> 01:19:42.860
MOMMY, THE BRIDGE!

01:19:43.028 --> 01:19:47.364
MOMMY, WATCH OUT!
WATCH OUT!

01:19:49.951 --> 01:19:51.202
UGH!

01:19:51.369 --> 01:19:53.287
OH, MY GOD!

01:19:53.747 --> 01:19:55.372
OH, MY GOD!

01:19:55.540 --> 01:19:57.374
BACK UP!

01:19:59.044 --> 01:20:01.504
HURRY!

01:20:04.216 --> 01:20:12.216
♪♪♪

01:20:14.810 --> 01:20:22.810
♪♪♪

01:20:38.542 --> 01:20:40.459
MOMMY, WE HAVE TO GET OUT!

01:20:40.627 --> 01:20:41.919
THE WATER'S RISING!

01:20:42.087 --> 01:20:43.462
W-WE HAVE TO GET OUT!

01:20:43.630 --> 01:20:45.256
WE CAN STILL GET OUT.

01:20:45.423 --> 01:20:48.175
YOU CAN SWIM.

01:20:48.343 --> 01:20:51.345
TAKE A DEEP BREATH,
AND I'LL OPEN THE WINDOW.

01:20:51.513 --> 01:20:53.347
MOMMY, I CAN'T!

01:20:53.515 --> 01:20:54.557
I'M AFRAID!

01:20:54.724 --> 01:20:55.850
I-I CAN'T!

01:20:56.017 --> 01:20:58.936
VIRGINIA, DO
WHAT MOMMY SAYS!

01:21:00.981 --> 01:21:06.151
GO ON, NOW, TAKE A DEEP
BREATH AND SWIM TO THE SURFACE.

01:21:06.903 --> 01:21:08.237
DO IT!

01:21:08.405 --> 01:21:10.030
GO!

01:21:48.820 --> 01:21:53.991
[BREATHING HEAVILY]

01:22:04.836 --> 01:22:11.967
[SCREAMING]

01:22:16.139 --> 01:22:17.806
NO!

01:22:17.974 --> 01:22:21.894
NOOO!
NOOO!

01:22:22.062 --> 01:22:23.437
DAVID!

01:22:23.605 --> 01:22:25.314
DAVID, HELP ME!

01:22:25.482 --> 01:22:26.774
HELP ME!

01:22:26.942 --> 01:22:28.651
GOD, HELP ME!

01:22:28.818 --> 01:22:30.277
DAVID!

01:22:30.445 --> 01:22:33.280
DAVID, HELP ME!

01:22:45.669 --> 01:22:49.088
[VIRGINIA CRYING]

01:22:50.006 --> 01:22:51.423
DAVID...

01:22:51.591 --> 01:22:55.344
DAVID, I KILLED HER.
I KILLED HER!

01:22:56.388 --> 01:22:58.931
SHE'S UPSTAIRS.
SHE'S IN THE BATHROOM.

01:22:59.099 --> 01:23:01.558
I KILLED HER.

01:23:01.726 --> 01:23:04.353
[CRYING]

01:23:04.521 --> 01:23:07.272
ALL RIGHT, COME ON!
COME ON!

01:23:07.816 --> 01:23:09.024
STOP!
DAVID!

01:23:09.192 --> 01:23:10.317
YOU COME ON!
YOU SHOW ME!

01:23:10.485 --> 01:23:11.485
SHE'S UPSTAIRS?

01:23:11.528 --> 01:23:13.487
YOU SHOW ME, YOU HEAR?!
COME ON!

01:23:13.655 --> 01:23:16.198
[SCREAMING]

01:23:18.910 --> 01:23:20.619
STOP!

01:23:20.787 --> 01:23:23.956
I DON'T WANT TO SEE HER!
STOP!

01:23:25.125 --> 01:23:26.291
[SCREAMING]
STOP!

01:23:26.459 --> 01:23:27.459
[GRUNTS]

01:23:27.627 --> 01:23:30.004
LOOK!
LOOK!

01:23:30.505 --> 01:23:31.672
LOOK!

01:23:31.840 --> 01:23:32.840
[SCREAMING STOPS]

01:23:32.882 --> 01:23:34.675
ALL RIGHT, LOOK AT THIS.
LOOK!

01:23:46.896 --> 01:23:54.896
♪♪♪

01:23:57.699 --> 01:23:59.366
HERE.

01:23:59.534 --> 01:24:01.076
THIS SHOULD WARM YOU UP.

01:24:01.244 --> 01:24:04.163
THANKS.

01:24:04.622 --> 01:24:07.207
HMM.

01:24:11.254 --> 01:24:14.673
UM...

01:24:15.300 --> 01:24:20.471
YOU KNOW, W-WE'RE
COMING VERY CLOSE, VIRGINIA.

01:24:20.638 --> 01:24:22.639
YOU SEE, TONIGHT YOU
REMEMBERED THE ACCIDENT

01:24:22.807 --> 01:24:26.393
AT THE BRIDGE, AND THAT'S
WHERE IT ALL STARTED.

01:24:26.561 --> 01:24:27.853
BUT DAVID, I
DON'T UNDERSTAND.

01:24:28.021 --> 01:24:29.563
WHY WOULD I
THINK I KILLED ANN?

01:24:29.731 --> 01:24:32.983
L-LISTEN, IT MAY BE VERY
PAINFUL, BUT YOU SEE,

01:24:33.151 --> 01:24:37.821
WE'VE GOT TO FIND THE LINK
BETWEEN YOUR TRAUMA...

01:24:37.989 --> 01:24:41.033
AND YOUR FRIENDS.

01:24:50.168 --> 01:24:53.045
BRIDGE...

01:24:54.339 --> 01:24:58.675
THE KIDS... THEY PLAY CHICKEN
ON THE BRIDGE AS IT GOES UP.

01:24:59.552 --> 01:25:03.013
THEY... THEY CALL IT A GAME.

01:25:03.181 --> 01:25:07.434
AND THEY TOOK
YOU OVER THE BRIDGE?

01:25:11.231 --> 01:25:15.859
IS THIS... IS
THIS ALL A GAME?

01:25:16.569 --> 01:25:19.113
IS IT?

01:25:19.280 --> 01:25:21.198
[SIGHS]

01:25:21.366 --> 01:25:26.578
I THINK I BETTER STAY HERE
UNTIL YOUR FATHER GETS HOME.

01:25:26.746 --> 01:25:28.413
[SIGHS]

01:25:28.581 --> 01:25:31.667
OKAY.

01:25:35.713 --> 01:25:38.632
IT'S MY BIRTHDAY.

01:25:40.552 --> 01:25:42.594
MMM, IT'S AFTER 12:00.

01:25:42.762 --> 01:25:45.514
SO IT IS.

01:25:46.933 --> 01:25:49.601
HAPPY BIRTHDAY, VIRGINIA.

01:26:00.822 --> 01:26:04.199
HAPPY BIRTHDAY.

01:26:12.208 --> 01:26:20.007
♪♪♪

01:26:20.175 --> 01:26:28.175
♪♪♪

01:26:35.190 --> 01:26:43.190
♪♪♪

01:26:59.714 --> 01:27:01.089
OH, HI, DOC.

01:27:01.257 --> 01:27:03.425
IS VIRGINIA WAINWRIGHT
AT HOME?

01:27:03.593 --> 01:27:05.636
OH, WELL, SHE HASN'T
BEEN FEELING VERY WELL.

01:27:05.803 --> 01:27:07.971
SHE'S SLEEPING.

01:27:08.139 --> 01:27:09.806
WE'RE INVESTIGATING
THE DISAPPEARANCE

01:27:09.974 --> 01:27:12.142
OF MISS ANN THOMERSON.

01:27:12.310 --> 01:27:15.020
WE FOUND HER CAR ABANDONED
JUST ACROSS THE ROAD.

01:27:15.188 --> 01:27:16.897
SHE HASN'T BEEN
SEEN SINCE YESTERDAY.

01:27:17.065 --> 01:27:19.185
HER PARENTS ARE AWAY, AND THE
ONLY INFORMATION WE HAVE

01:27:19.275 --> 01:27:21.026
IS THAT SHE WAS ON
HER WAY OVER HERE.

01:27:21.194 --> 01:27:25.697
YES, UH... WELL, UH, I-I'VE
BEEN HERE ALL WEEKEND, AND I

01:27:25.865 --> 01:27:28.992
KNOW THAT MISS WAINWRIGHT
HAS NOT HAD ANY VISITORS.

01:27:29.160 --> 01:27:33.664
I WOULD LIKE TO ASK MISS
WAINWRIGHT SOME QUESTIONS.

01:27:33.831 --> 01:27:35.165
WELL, SUPPOSE I HAVE
HER GIVE YOU A RING

01:27:35.333 --> 01:27:36.583
WHEN SHE WAKES UP.

01:27:36.751 --> 01:27:37.876
IS THAT ALL RIGHT?

01:27:38.044 --> 01:27:39.211
OKAY, FINE.

01:27:39.379 --> 01:27:41.171
HERE'S MY CARD.

01:27:41.339 --> 01:27:44.341
OH, DOC, ALMOST
STOLE YOUR PAPER.

01:27:44.509 --> 01:27:46.009
OH, YES, THANK YOU.

01:27:46.177 --> 01:27:49.179
THANK YOU.

01:27:49.555 --> 01:27:57.555
♪♪♪

01:28:01.276 --> 01:28:02.985
VIRGINIA.

01:28:03.152 --> 01:28:08.407
VIRGINIA, THE POLICE WERE
JUST HERE, AND THEY FOUND, UH,

01:28:08.574 --> 01:28:09.992
THEY FOUND ANN'S CAR.

01:28:10.159 --> 01:28:11.910
SHE'S MISSING.

01:28:12.078 --> 01:28:13.120
OH, MY GOD!

01:28:13.288 --> 01:28:14.246
THEN I DID KILL HER!
I KILLED ANN!

01:28:14.414 --> 01:28:16.623
LISTEN! WAIT! WAIT!
JUST A MINUTE!

01:28:16.791 --> 01:28:21.628
SHE'S MISSING...
THAT'S ALL.

01:28:21.796 --> 01:28:25.299
THEY'RE ALL JUST MISSING.

01:28:25.466 --> 01:28:28.093
[GROANING]

01:28:29.804 --> 01:28:32.764
DAVID, I-I DON'T UNDERSTAND.

01:28:32.932 --> 01:28:35.267
WHAT... WHAT
DOES IT ALL MEAN?

01:28:35.435 --> 01:28:39.021
I THINK, UH, IT MEANS THAT
IT'S LOCKED UP IN YOUR PAST,

01:28:39.188 --> 01:28:42.357
AND YOU'VE GOT TO
TRY TO GO BACK.

01:28:45.111 --> 01:28:47.988
WHAT DO THESE PEOPLE HAVE
TO DO WITH THE WHOLE THING...

01:28:48.156 --> 01:28:52.117
ALFRED, STEVE, GREG,
BERNADETTE, ETIENNE?

01:28:52.285 --> 01:28:55.162
WHAT HAPPENED
BEFORE THE ACCIDENT?

01:28:55.330 --> 01:28:58.832
YOU'VE GOT TO
TRY TO REMEMBER.

01:28:59.417 --> 01:29:01.418
VIRGINIA: IT
WAS MY BIRTHDAY.

01:29:01.586 --> 01:29:04.838
MOTHER DECIDED TO HAVE
MY PARTY IN THE COTTAGE.

01:29:05.006 --> 01:29:07.257
BERNADETTE O'HARA,
ETIENNE VERCOURS,

01:29:07.425 --> 01:29:11.178
STEVE MAXWELL, ALFRED MORRIS,
GREG HELLMAN,

01:29:11.346 --> 01:29:14.473
AND ANN THOMERSON...
SIX OF THE RICHEST.

01:29:14.640 --> 01:29:17.142
NOTHING BUT THE
BEST FOR MY LITTLE GIRL.

01:29:17.310 --> 01:29:18.560
IT'S ALMOST 5:00.

01:29:18.728 --> 01:29:20.187
DID YOU TELL
THEM TO COME AT 4:00?

01:29:20.355 --> 01:29:21.897
YES, MOMMY.

01:29:22.065 --> 01:29:25.025
I SUPPOSE THIS IS WHAT
THEY CALL "FASHIONABLY LATE."

01:29:25.193 --> 01:29:26.860
[THUNDER RUMBLES]

01:29:27.028 --> 01:29:28.362
SHIT!

01:29:28.529 --> 01:29:31.615
[TELEPHONE RINGS]

01:29:31.783 --> 01:29:33.116
HELLO?

01:29:33.284 --> 01:29:34.576
MR. WAINWRIGHT: I'VE BEEN
TRYING TO CALL YOU ALL DAY.

01:29:34.744 --> 01:29:36.104
I CAN'T GET HOME
UNTIL THE WEEKEND.

01:29:36.120 --> 01:29:37.579
WOULD YOU TELL GINNIE
I'LL MAKE IT UP TO HER?

01:29:37.747 --> 01:29:40.165
TELL HER YOURSELF,
YOU BASTARD!

01:29:40.333 --> 01:29:42.751
IT'S YOUR LOVING FATHER.

01:29:50.093 --> 01:29:51.593
HELLO?

01:29:51.761 --> 01:29:53.220
HAPPY BIRTHDAY, SWEETHEART.

01:29:53.388 --> 01:29:54.888
DADDY, WHERE ARE YOU?

01:29:55.056 --> 01:29:57.682
