01:30:20.832 --> 01:30:22.082
GOODBYE, SWEETHEART.

01:30:22.250 --> 01:30:25.127
GOODBYE, DADDY.

01:30:26.170 --> 01:30:28.713
WHY DID YOU SAY THAT,
VIRGINIA... THAT YOUR FRIENDS

01:30:28.881 --> 01:30:31.007
WERE HERE?

01:30:31.175 --> 01:30:34.261
